{"tid":1457154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【致一班屌手足大力過屌政府嘅人】走咗咪約個時間入返去囉好撚難咩？","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:29:21.000Z","uid":2565,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3581fa62bb8495562074ac44f11ccbdc8e94dd","tid":1457154,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"有咩好屌<br />\n係都要屌自己友<br />\n依家走咗無得返去咩？<br />\n機場以後無得入去啊？<br />\n機場以後唔開放啊？<br />\n以後唔畀人接機啊？<br />\n<br />\n好似五年前咁囉<br />\n屌囉<br />\n勇武又屌撚晒啲和理非囉<br />\n和理非又捉鳩晒啲鬼囉<br />\n好勁啊屌到證明到自己啱撚晒喇<br />\n威啦咁<br />\n屌咗個民主返嚟喇<br />\n<br />\n咁樣政府唔會輸㗎喎：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔走就現實清你場<br />\n走又上網笑鳩你走</span></span><br />\n屌嚟根本無意思<br />\n<br />\n「人多就無事」依個更加係都市傳說<br />\n400打20都輸啦<br />\n一清場就鳩跑<br />\n人多有咩優勢啊？<br />\n係啊，係你跑嗰陣會跑慢咗囉，<br />\n好撚大優勢㗎。<br />\n<br />\n屌屌屌屌屌<br />\n一係打<br />\n一係閃啦<br />\n打又唔撚打<br />\n閃又唔撚閃<br />\n做乜鳩"},{"pid":"808f808408b7f0575e6a41e455357b11bc257f59","tid":1457154,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"戰又不戰 <br />\n退又不退"},{"pid":"b18bbf8eb55365c046dfd778822fb1de9926f21e","tid":1457154,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"屌啊"},{"pid":"328daf6f0e5617ba2c3a5ec27ae61b2bed03e02e","tid":1457154,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"134a84785933326c581f1f5702a4456db2e11608","tid":1457154,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"50e715b088f7c8d15c0225df4d93fc02ac600471","tid":1457154,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"30a735e61cca3854af2bf9256ad179616140a34f","tid":